System made by Russell Edward Timóteo Torres.
Hey, I'm Russell and i'm 17 years old. I have always been interested in exact sciences, in music, e-games and in the functioning of new technologies. In Mathematics Kumon, I was a Silver medal (2015-2016) and Gold medal (2017), when I also received the 'Liga I' trophy. I've been assisting with sound design in my church for about 5 years, and more recently I've coordinated the transmission of live streams. At the age of 15, I started working at Internews in the QA area, in Web and Desktop systems. Upon entering the IFNMG I had to stop work due to full-time classes, and currently, I do Computer Technician.
